js-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fxg1665703107194.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fxg1665703107194.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fxg1665703107194.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fxg1665703107194\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                              \n Control Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fxg1665703107194__ul_acm_lzg_bxb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uha1665703107266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uha1665703107266.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the text describing an image in a static server page. It sets the alt attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Alternative Text (u_alt)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nfw1665703107564.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nfw1665703107564.html\" title=\"This widget property defines how an image is aligned within the field in a static server page. It sets the align attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Alignment (u_align)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rks1665703107638.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rks1665703107638.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the width of a border, in pixels, that surrounds an image. This property sets the border attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Border (u_border)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rnt1665703107711.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rnt1665703107711.html\" title=\"Widget property that specifies the width of a text area in a static server page in number of characters.\">Columns (cols)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hjb1665703107869.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjb1665703107869.html\" title=\"Widget property that specifies the height of the displayed image in a static server page as a number of pixels, or as a percentage of the original image height. This property sets the height attribute of an &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout and the image is scaled to fit.\">Height (u_height)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pne1665703108090.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pne1665703108090.html\" title=\"In a static server page, exclude the field or entity if it does not need to be sent to the browser.\">Exclude</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efb1665703108245.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efb1665703108245.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the number of pixels of white space to be inserted to the left and right of the image. This property sets the hspace attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Horizontal Spaces (u_hspace)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"npf1665703108397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npf1665703108397.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Image Source (u_src)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmf1665703108475.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmf1665703108475.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page.\">Link Text (u_hyperldispl)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twd1665703108686.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twd1665703108686.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page.\">Link Value (u_url)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qbx1665703108990.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbx1665703108990.html\" title=\"Property that specifies the height of the Text Area in a static server page as rows of characters.\">Rows (rows)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pqj1665703109065.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pqj1665703109065.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the path and file name of a low-resolution image to display in the server page while the main image is loading. It sets the lowsrc attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Shadow Image (u_lowsrc)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbk1665703109209.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbk1665703109209.html\" title=\"Size of the text control, in characters.\">Size</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqu1665703109428.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqu1665703109428.html\" title=\"Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded.\">Target Window (u_target)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oco1665703109723.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oco1665703109723.html\" title=\"This property defines ValRep list for the static server page widget.\">Value/Representation</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usg1665703109942.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usg1665703109942.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the number of pixels of white space to be inserted above and below the image in a static server page. It sets the vspace attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Vertical Spaces (u_vspace)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cdk1665703110016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cdk1665703110016.html\" title=\"Widget property that determines whether to reconnect the data field occurrences in the static server page to their database counterparts.\">Webget Synchronization (sync)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sba1665703110233.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sba1665703110233.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the width of the displayed image in a static server page. It sets the width attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Width (u_width)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613157\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613157\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Control Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Control Properties Alternative Text (u_alt) Alignment (u_align) Border (u_border) Columns (cols) Height (u_height) Exclude Horizontal Spaces (u_hspace) Image Source (u_src) Link Text (u_hyperldispl) Link Value (u_url) Rows (rows) Shadow Image (u_lowsrc) Size Target Window (u_target) Value/Representation Vertical Spaces (u_vspace) Webget Synchronization (sync) Width (u_width) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}